&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In both cases, tukituki writes individual process logs to &lt;code&gt;.tukituki/logs/&lt;/code&gt; as usual, and you can inspect them with &lt;code&gt;tukituki logs &amp;lt;name&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; at any time.&lt;/p&gt;

